An implementation of the model object 'Node Type'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Node Parameter
  • Metadata
  • Persistant Data
  • Component Name
  • Offset Label X
  • Offset Label Y
  • Pos X
  • Pos Y
  • Unique Name
